Important Information:
The default bank balance is set at 50000.
The ATM balance is set at 20000.
The PIN is harcoded to be '1234'.
The ATM can only allow withdrawals in the multiples of 50.
There are only a specific set of denominations set inside the ATM which can be seen in the withdrawal screen of the ATM.
There is a timeout for screen changes harcoded into the program.
There is a beep function integrated into the program which uses the 'windows.h' header and may not work on all systems and may throw and error.

All the above details can be changed in the code of the program, so feel free to change as per your will!
